---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - ELVIRA" 
  description="Learn about ELVIRA's privacy practices and how we protect hotel and guest information."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 border-b pb-4" data-i18n="privacy.title">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600" data-i18n="privacy.lastUpdated">Last Updated: June 1, 2025</p>
      
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-8 prose prose-blue max-w-none text-justify">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.introduction">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.introduction.p1">
            ELVIRA ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our digital concierge platform, website, and services.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.introduction.p2">
            We take data privacy seriously, especially in the hospitality industry where trust is paramount. Our platform is built around the principle of minimizing personal data collection while maximizing service quality.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.collection">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner">2.1 Hotel Partner Information</h3>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner.intro">
            For hotels using our platform, we collect:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner.item1">Business contact information (names, email addresses, phone numbers)</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner.item2">Hotel details (address, number of rooms, services offered)</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner.item3">Payment information for billing purposes</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.hotelPartner.item4">Login credentials for the management dashboard</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest">2.2 End User (Guest) Information</h3>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.intro">
            Our platform is designed with privacy in mind. For hotel guests using our service, we collect minimal information:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.item1">Room number (temporarily associated with the session)</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.item2">Session verification code</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.item3">Service requests and preferences during their stay</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.item4">Chat communications with hotel staff</li>
          </ul>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.collection.guest.note">
            Importantly, we do not collect personal identification information from guests. The system operates on anonymous, room-based sessions that expire after checkout.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic">2.3 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic.intro">
            When you access our platform, we may automatically collect:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic.item1">Device information (type, operating system, browser)</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic.item2">Usage data and patterns</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic.item3">IP address and approximate location</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.collection.automatic.item4">Cookies and similar technologies (see our Cookie Policy)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.usage">3. How We Use Information</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.usage.intro">We use the collected information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item1">Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item2">Process transactions and fulfill service requests</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item3">Communicate with hotel partners about their account</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item4">Respond to inquiries and provide support</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item5">Monitor and analyze usage patterns and trends</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item6">Protect against unauthorized access and ensure platform security</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.usage.item7">Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.sharing">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.sharing.intro">We may share information in the following circumstances:</p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.sharing.item1"><strong>Hotel Partners:</strong> Guest service requests and communications are shared with the relevant hotel staff to fulfill requests.</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.sharing.item2"><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We engage trusted third parties to help us operate our business (e.g., hosting, analytics, payment processing).</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.sharing.item3"><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law, regulation, or legal process.</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.sharing.item4"><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> If ELVIRA is involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.</li>
          </ul>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.sharing.note">We do not sell or rent user data to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.security">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.security.p1">
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no electronic transmission or storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.transfers">6. International Transfers</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.transfers.p1">
            Our services may be hosted and processed in various countries, including outside your country of residence. By using our services, you consent to the transfer of your information to countries that may have different data protection rules than your country.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.retention">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.retention.p1">
            We retain hotel partner information for as long as necessary to provide our services and fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Guest session data is automatically deleted after checkout plus a brief retention period for service quality and security purposes.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.rights">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.rights.intro">Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your information, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.rights.item1">Accessing, correcting, or deleting your information</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.rights.item2">Objecting to certain processing activities</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.rights.item3">Requesting restriction of processing</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.rights.item4">Data portability</li>
            <li data-i18n="privacy.rights.item5">Withdrawing consent</li>
          </ul>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.rights.contact">To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided at the end of this policy.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.children">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.children.p1">
            Our services are not intended for children under 16 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.changes">10. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.changes.p1">
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy frequently.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.contact">11. Contact Us</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.contact.intro">
            If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="privacy.contact.company">ELVIRA</span><br>
            <span data-i18n="privacy.contact.address1">Wedekinstasse 25</span><br>
            <span data-i18n="privacy.contact.address2">Berlin, Germany</span><br>
            <span data-i18n="privacy.contact.email">Email: privacy@ELVIRA.com</span><br>
            <span data-i18n="privacy.contact.phone">Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</span>
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.sections.faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.faq.dataProtection.question">How is my data protected?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600" data-i18n="privacy.faq.dataProtection.answer">We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your data.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900" data-i18n="privacy.faq.dataCollection.question">What data do you collect?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600" data-i18n="privacy.faq.dataCollection.answer">We only collect essential data needed to provide our services.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>